These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: lemon, grapefruit, cabbage, kale
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, guinea-pig, frog, rat
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, skateboard, roller, train
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the person driving the train is the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the far left##1
4. the person eating lemon is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person driving the roller and the person eating grapefruit##2
6. the person driving the skateboard is the owner of the frog##1
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | cabbage | kale  | grapefruit | lemon  |
| Pet         | rat    | guinea-pig  | hedgehog       | frog     |
| Transport   | roller     | tram | train       | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, hiking, skydiving, board-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, romance, spy, time-travel
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, rugby, weightlifting, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
5. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
7. the person watching spy movies is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | hiking | collecting    | board-games  | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | thriller  | romance   | spy    |
| Sport         | rugby | tennis | parkour | weightlifting      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, water, cola, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, drawing, camping, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, salsa, gospel, d&b
1. the fan of salsa is between the fan of d&b and the person drinking water##2
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the fan of classical##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1
6. the fan of classical is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
7. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | water | hot-chocolate         | soy-milk   | cola    |
| Hobby         | drawing | rock-climbing | singing | camping |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | salsa        | d&b      | classical   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, indonesian, pakistani, turkish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, lacrosse, parkour, swimming
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, quad-bike, boat, trike
1. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the trike and the turkish##2
3. the pakistani is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the pakistani is on the right of the argentine##1
6. the person driving the trike is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | turkish        | indonesian   | argentine | pakistani |
| Sport         | parkour | basketball | lacrosse    | swimming |
| Transport     | boat       | roller     | trike       | quad-bike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, mirinda, coffee, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, collecting, singing, card-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, ice-hockey, water-polo, badminton
1. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking mirinda##2
2. the person who's sport is badminton is the person drinking milk##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's hobby is dancing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | sprite | milk      | mirinda       | coffee   |
| Hobby      | dancing   | collecting  | card-games | singing     |
| Sport      | ice-hockey     | badminton | water-polo        | soccer |

