.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, pepper, orange, grapes
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, board-games, skydiving, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, skiing, water-polo, climbing
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
6. the person eating pepper is between the person eating blueberry and the person eating orange##2
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | orange | pepper  | blueberry | grapes      |
| Hobby   | skydiving  | woodworking  | puzzles | board-games |
| Sport   | climbing | baseball | skiing | water-polo     |

