.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, radish, plum, zucchini
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, crime, adventure, fantasy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, basketball, swimming, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is the person watching family movies##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the person eating plum is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the person eating radish is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching adventure movies##2
7. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | plum  | radish    | zucchini | orange  |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | fantasy       | crime        | family    |
| Sport         | basketball | golf | skiing  | swimming |

