The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, satire, epic, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: goat, pony, rat, ferret
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person watching satire movies is between the owner of the ferret and the person who's hobby is photography##2
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | hiking  | photography | fishing | drawing |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | time-travel | satire   | epic         |
| Pet           | goat | rat  | pony   | ferret      |

