1. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of metal##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person eating avocado##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person eating peas##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person eating peas##1
5. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the fan of r&b and the person who's hobby is baking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | asparagus  | avocado    | orange | peas       |
| Hobby         | dancing | hiking | baking  | singing |
| Music-Genre   | r&b   | metal      | electronic  | dubstep     |

