4. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
6. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
7. the person watching documentary movies is the person who's hobby is reading##1
8. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person eating kiwi##1

