.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, cauliflower, zucchini, plum
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, video-games, woodworking, skydiving
4 different pets are kept: pony, lizard, mouse, snake
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating peach##1
2. the owner of the mouse is the person eating cauliflower##1
3. the owner of the pony is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the owner of the pony and the person eating plum##2
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the owner of the snake##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is the owner of the lizard##1
7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | plum  | zucchini | peach | cauliflower     |
| Hobby   | card-games | woodworking   | skydiving  | video-games    |
| Pet     | lizard        | snake       | pony      | mouse |

