.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, cola, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, cooking, writing, magic-tricks
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, mouse, snake
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking cola and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | cola     | iced-tea | milk       |
| Hobby      | writing  | magic-tricks | photography  | cooking |
| Pet        | snake  | guinea-pig      | mouse        | chinchilla      |

