3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the lizard##1
5. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | mirinda | soy-milk  | iced-tea       | 7up   |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks     | traveling | sudoku | woodworking |
| Pet        | lizard        | dog | bird     | fish |

