The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, adventure, superhero, epic
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, car, skateboard, quad-bike
1. the person watching sports movies is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is the pilot##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the paramedic##1
4. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the car is between the person watching superhero movies and the pilot##2
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the car is the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job           | electrician | project-manager | pilot    | paramedic   |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero      | adventure   | epic | sports |
| Transport     | subway     | car       | skateboard        | quad-bike    |

