.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, magic-tricks, reading, puzzles
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, nurse, engineer, freelancer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, cricket, cycling, skiing
1. the person who's hobby is reading is the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the freelancer##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is between the lawyer and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
6. the engineer is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
7. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is cricket##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Hobby   | reading   | magic-tricks           | sudoku         | puzzles      |
| Job     | lawyer | engineer | freelancer | nurse |
| Sport   | cycling     | cricket         | tennis       | skiing        |

