.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, tea, fanta
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, trance, electronic, disco
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, pakistani, french
1. the fan of jazz is the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking tea and the brazilian##2
3. the person drinking tea is the fan of trance##1
4. the person drinking tea is between the fan of electronic and the french##2
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
6. the argentine is between the pakistani and the fan of disco##2
7. the fan of jazz is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage      | 7up | tea | coffee   | fanta |
| Music-Genre   | jazz  | trance    | electronic   | disco     |
| Nationality   | french  | pakistani | argentine | brazilian   |

