There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, juice, cola, fanta
There 4 different types of food: tomato, apple, kale, banana
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, badminton, volleyball, basketball
1. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
2. the person eating kale is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1
5. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
6. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating kale##1
7. the person drinking cola is the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite    | juice | fanta           | cola |
| Food       | tomato | kale    | apple          | banana   |
| Sport      | volleyball  | badminton   | basketball | water-polo  |

