.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite, almond-milk, cola
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, musical, action, zombie
4 different pets are kept: snake, rat, fish, pony
1. the person watching action movies is the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is between the person watching action movies and the person watching western movies##2
5. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
6. the owner of the pony is between the person drinking sprite and the owner of the snake##2
7. the person watching zombie movies is the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | mirinda | sprite     | cola   |
| Movie-Genre   | western | zombie        | action  | musical  |
| Pet           | snake      | pony         | rat | fish |

