3. the software-developer is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is the chef##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person driving the skateboard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | software-developer        | chef  | bartender | nurse   |
| Sport       | badminton | baseball | cricket    | rugby |
| Transport   | jet-ski        | skateboard     | helicopter       | quad-bike      |

