.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, pumpkin, tomato, avocado
4 different pets are kept: dog, lizard, horse, ferret
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, trike, airplane, subway
1. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
2. the person eating garlic is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
4. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the subway is the owner of the ferret##1
6. the owner of the lizard is between the person eating avocado and the person driving the airplane##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | avocado | pumpkin | garlic | tomato |
| Pet         | dog       | lizard     | horse   | ferret   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | trike | airplane | subway |

 